{"tid":1792404,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"葉門 死撚左","createTime":"2019-12-21T15:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T15:42:28.000Z","uid":7814,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"34e2cde7a8c6554db365e79e47e57a56ae5dc62e","tid":1792404,"uid":7814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"葉問個仔學校打交被趕出校，佢自己又確診cancer<br />\n<br />\n飛去美國幫仔搵學校，華人受歧視欺凌，葉問制止欺凌，得罪美軍陸戰隊軍官。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍美國出書、收鬼佬徙弟教功夫，引起唐人街華人武術界不滿。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍有美軍徒弟想將詠春引入部隊，受空手道教官打壓，派人去唐人街踢館，被葉問狠狠教訓。<br />\n<br />\n美國軍官同時派人打傷大量唐人街武師，搵移民局拉人。最後葉問入軍營挑機，打贏軍官。最後放棄個仔留學計劃，親自教個仔詠春。最後病發身亡。"},{"pid":"061107732ab71486487104db2b147b0591264fb8","tid":1792404,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZM3zeQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZM3zeQ.jpg&h=9e6168b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尊重知識産權，強烈反對侵權行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">傳送門：</span><a href=\"https://pttplay.com/vod-detail-id-RwdaV.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpttplay.com%2Fvod-detail-id-RwdaV.html&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3AwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=702a149a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pttplay.com/vod-detail-id-RwdaV.html</a>"},{"pid":"03fe017edc4fbaffbf5ccf850df5db4684cf34fe","tid":1792404,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:32:11.000Z","msg":"【天佑香港人】22/12 促成世界性「撐東突厥斯坦」民意風暴！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eFNMCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eFNMCS</a>"},{"pid":"660c6cf87ad2f42124191e734ed00a8cd3dee1ee","tid":1792404,"uid":318369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JB4pjrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJB4pjrg.jpg